text:
Within days of Rohit Sharma calling time on his Test career, Virat Kohli too followed suit and retired before next month’s tour to England. Was he quick to read the room after the abrupt end to Rohit’s Test innings? With talk of Shubman Gill’s early coronation at 25 did he sense palace intrigue and a subtle signal to him? Or was it the case of the 36-year-old father of two no longer having that famous drive in him to deal with the demons in the head that mess up your muscle memory?
